{"pageProps":{"note":{"id":"12tecdg3zv9o1g60kax26yi","title":"Sampling","desc":"","updated":1704867589042,"created":1704867517865,"custom":{},"fname":"development.mlops.data.sampling","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":"repos/dendron-aws-vault","remote":{"type":"git","url":"https://github.com/cczhong11/my_note.git"},"name":"my_note"},"contentHash":"e605eddf3b7a39a2daf434bd6f35a1c6","links":[],"anchors":{"如何创建训练数据":{"type":"header","text":"如何创建训练数据","value":"如何创建训练数据","line":8,"column":0,"depth":2},"选择训练数据的抽样方法":{"type":"header","text":"选择训练数据的抽样方法","value":"选择训练数据的抽样方法","line":10,"column":0,"depth":3},"非概率抽样方法":{"type":"header","text":"非概率抽样方法","value":"非概率抽样方法","line":14,"column":0,"depth":4},"随机抽样方法":{"type":"header","text":"随机抽样方法","value":"随机抽样方法","line":28,"column":0,"depth":4}},"children":[],"parent":"qserrgt70scz4ieugup6b5r","data":{}},"body":"<h1 id=\"sampling\">Sampling<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#sampling\"></a></h1>\n<h2 id=\"如何创建训练数据\">如何创建训练数据<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#如何创建训练数据\"></a></h2>\n<h3 id=\"选择训练数据的抽样方法\">选择训练数据的抽样方法<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#选择训练数据的抽样方法\"></a></h3>\n<p>由于无法获取所有真实世界的数据，我们需要从中抽取一部分进行训练。关键在于如何实现有效的抽样。抽样方法大致分为两类：非概率抽样和随机抽样。</p>\n<h4 id=\"非概率抽样方法\">非概率抽样方法<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#非概率抽样方法\"></a></h4>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p><strong>便利抽样</strong>（Convenience Sampling）<br>\n主要基于数据的可获取性。</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>雪球抽样</strong>（Snowball Sampling）<br>\n以已有的样本为基础，逐渐扩大样本范围，类似于深度优先搜索（DFS）算法。</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>判断抽样</strong>（Judgmental Sampling）<br>\n由专家根据经验决定抽样方法。</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>配额抽样</strong>（Quota Sampling）<br>\n在每个类别中选择固定数量的样本进行调查。</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h4 id=\"随机抽样方法\">随机抽样方法<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#随机抽样方法\"></a></h4>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p><strong>简单随机抽样</strong><br>\n随机选择数据的一个子集，例如随机选取10%的数据。</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>分层抽样</strong>（Stratified Sampling）<br>\n从不同的类别（如A和B）中各选取一定比例，如1%，以确保包含这些类别的数据。</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>加权抽样</strong>（Weighted Sampling）<br>\n对每个样本赋予不同的权重，代表其被抽中的可能性。</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>保留抽样</strong>（Reservoir Sampling）<br>\n适用于流数据。初始选择K个元素，对于新到的第N个元素，生成1到N之间的随机数。如果这个数在1到K之间，用第N个元素替换对应位置的元素。</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>重要性抽样</strong>（Importance Sampling）<br>\n当从一个分布P抽样成本很高时，可以使用一个替代的分布Q进行抽样，然后根据权重调整样本。</p>\n</li>\n</ol>","noteIndex":{"id":"0f1b48c7-3a25-4016-83a5-15864d7803ad","title":"Development","vault":{"fsPath":"repos/dendron-aws-vault","remote":{"type":"git","url":"https://github.com/cczhong11/my_note.git"},"name":"my_note"},"type":"note","desc":"","links":[{"from":{"fname":"root","id":"c95dc4f5-23db-45e7-a15b-64582a183ccc","vaultName":"my_note"},"type":"backlink","position":{"start":{"line":8,"column":3,"offset":63},"end":{"line":8,"column":21,"offset":81},"indent":[]},"value":"development"}],"anchors":{},"fname":"development","updated":1618381238346,"created":1612940782409,"parent":null,"children":["400115e9-30f7-4a13-9776-db059bc9cd42","xsX5v3ZsyJ0i6gf9","1bc3b45a-b6f4-4150-87d3-5bd5b6eb8c24","6cea4852-6e7c-4140-b476-85c07b48a642","a40ef849-d301-4d74-a778-e6d9469dfb5d","09d9081f-3dff-453d-8488-7d2344cc8895","p11phg7nb10yw0wck1fyagq","92917ea3-452e-48dc-875e-5cd0002041db","2e151826-cb22-4d89-8ce0-71dad7204ce8","baa39444-0da9-4c55-8df7-2a6f8f787fa4","q4um3bc3st86ilkkvdjom6x","62daf50d-a39e-463f-aabd-be53790281fd","3524d0a7-be73-45d6-847e-c970f5c1c760","eac0f243-05b3-4b95-bec3-848e33edbc40","zrjuka02gkzrqxt5djp2aws"],"data":{},"custom":{"nav_order":0,"permalink":"/"},"body":"\n","contentHash":"38357962f5a50c6fd7d318dfa66bea90"},"collectionChildren":null,"customHeadContent":null,"config":{"version":5,"dev":{"previewV2Enabled":false,"enablePreviewV2":true},"commands":{"lookup":{"note":{"selectionMode":"extract","confirmVaultOnCreate":false,"leaveTrace":false,"bubbleUpCreateNew":true,"fuzzThreshold":0.2,"vaultSelectionModeOnCreate":"smart"}},"insertNote":{"i